@startuml
skinparam actor {
  BorderColor DarkBlue
  BackgroundColor LightBlue
  FontSize 14
}
skinparam usecase {
  BorderColor Green
  BackgroundColor LightGreen
  FontSize 14
}
skinparam titleFontSize 24
skinparam noteBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam noteBorderColor DarkRed

title USECASE#5: View Population Breakdown by Continent

actor "Data Analyst" as User
rectangle "Population Report System" {
  usecase "View Population Breakdown by Continent" as UC5
}

User --> UC5 : Requests report

note right of UC5 : **Output:**\n- Continent\n- Total population\n- City population (%)\n- Non-city population (%)

note left of UC5 : **Extensions:**\n- Database failure: Display error message\n- No data found: Display "No population data available"\n- Calculation error: Log error and notify user
@enduml
